title: Days of our Lives Wed, Jul 17, 2013
description:
Adrienne is about to talk to Sami about the video of her attacking Bernardi but before she can, Sami makes things worse.


Nicole is touched when she learns how Eric has tried to protect her.


Kristen reaffirms her plans.


Kristen makes an important call to a man of the cloth.


Brady asks John for the truth about what happened with between his father and his ex the night of the seduction.


Will feels like a third wheel as Sonny works with Brent on a new project.
